thread.title: Atresmedia FY Net Profit Up 10 Pct At 142.1 Million Euros YoY

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Atresmedia FY Net Profit Up 10 Pct At 142.1 Million Euros YoY
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - ATRESMEDIA CORPORACION DE MEDIOS DE COMUNICACION SA:
* SAID ON WEDNESDAY FY NET PROFIT 142.1 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 129.1 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY NET SALES 983.9 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 962.6 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* FY EBITDA 202.1 MILLION EUROS VERSUS 201.9 MILLION EUROS YEAR AGO
* PROPOSES COMPLEMENTARY DIVIDEND OF 0.30 EUROS PER SHARE Source text for Eikon:
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
